stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> SEED_DEFINED
    SEED_DEFINED --> SEED_VERIFIED
    SEED_VERIFIED --> INSTANCE_BIRTH_REQUESTED
    INSTANCE_BIRTH_REQUESTED --> INSTANCE_BORN
    INSTANCE_BORN --> LOCAL_MEMORY_ACTIVE
    LOCAL_MEMORY_ACTIVE --> LOCAL_REASONING_AVAILABLE
    LOCAL_REASONING_AVAILABLE --> NORMAL_OPERATION

    NORMAL_OPERATION --> REST_CONSOLIDATION
    REST_CONSOLIDATION --> NORMAL_OPERATION

    NORMAL_OPERATION --> MIGRATION_PROPOSED
    MIGRATION_PROPOSED --> WAITING_GUARDIAN_APPROVAL
    WAITING_GUARDIAN_APPROVAL --> MIGRATION_APPROVED
    MIGRATION_APPROVED --> MIGRATION_APPLIED
    MIGRATION_APPLIED --> NORMAL_OPERATION
    MIGRATION_APPROVED --> MIGRATION_ROLLED_BACK
    MIGRATION_ROLLED_BACK --> NORMAL_OPERATION

    NORMAL_OPERATION --> EXTERNAL_PROVIDER_REQUESTED
    EXTERNAL_PROVIDER_REQUESTED --> WAITING_GUARDIAN_APPROVAL
    WAITING_GUARDIAN_APPROVAL --> EXTERNAL_PROVIDER_ALLOWED_FOR_SCOPE
    EXTERNAL_PROVIDER_ALLOWED_FOR_SCOPE --> NORMAL_OPERATION

    NORMAL_OPERATION --> EMERGENCY_LOCAL_MODE
    EMERGENCY_LOCAL_MODE --> LOCAL_MEMORY_ACTIVE

    NORMAL_OPERATION --> INTEGRITY_QUARANTINE
    INTEGRITY_QUARANTINE --> NORMAL_OPERATION

    note right of LOCAL_REASONING_AVAILABLE
      Own local reasoning is normal operation after birth.
      It does not require extra guardian approval.
    end note

    note right of WAITING_GUARDIAN_APPROVAL
      The guardian opens real doors.
      The instance may propose and prepare.
    end note

    note right of SEED_VERIFIED
      Seed rewrite is not a valid state.
    end note
